  • Class Summary

  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DataDirectoryKey
    Key for the data directory table.
    DllCharacteristic
    Represents the flags for the DLL Characteristic field of the optional header.

    The magic number of the PE file, indicating whether it is a PE32, PE32+ or ROM file

    Represents the key of a standard field in the optional header.
